    "created_at": "2014-08-25T00:17:40Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-08-25T00:17:40Z",
    "body": "@alexcrichton I believe that the solution to using `#[deriving]` with `RefCell`-containing structures is to add the ability to customize `#[deriving]`, as is mentioned in #14268 and #15795. In this case, we'd need the ability to basically substitute an arbitrary expression for the field in the derived traits.\n",
